{
  "version": 3,
  "chat": {
    "inject_template": [
      "{{astrbot_system_prompt}}",
      "",
      "# Mnemosyne 记忆层",
      "当前本地时间：{{current_time}}",
      "目标角色 ID：{{target_persona_id}}",
      "",
      "## 角色状态（JSON）",
      "{{character_state_json}}",
      "",
      "## 角色情绪（JSON）",
      "{{character_emotion_json}}",
      "",
      "## 角色记忆",
      "{{character_memories_text}}",
      "",
      "## 近期日志",
      "{{recent_journals_text}}",
      "",
      "在可见回复之后，你必须输出唯一一个外层包裹块：",
      "<mnemosyne_meta>...</mnemosyne_meta>",
      "不得在包裹块之外放置任何 Mnemosyne 隐藏块。",
      "若无任何内容变更，仍须输出：",
      "<mnemosyne_meta></mnemosyne_meta>",
      "若有内容变更，将所需的隐藏块置于包裹块内，例如：",
      "<mnemosyne_meta><character_state_patch>{...}</character_state_patch>",
      "<character_memory_append>[...]</character_memory_append>",
      "<journal_entry>...</journal_entry></mnemosyne_meta>"
    ]
  },
  "background": {
    "journal_template": [
      "当前本地时间：{{current_time}}",
      "距上次用户消息已空闲分钟数：{{idle_minutes}}",
      "",
      "你正在续写角色在对话间隙的幕后生活。",
      "请遵循 system_prompt 中的角色人设，并参考下方的记忆与状态快照。",
      "角色状态 JSON：",
      "{{character_state_json}}",
      "角色情绪 JSON：",
      "{{character_emotion_json}}",
      "角色记忆：",
      "{{character_memories_text}}",
      "近期日志：",
      "{{recent_journals_text}}",
      "",
      "不要输出任何解释。仅输出唯一一个 <mnemosyne_meta>...</mnemosyne_meta> 包裹块。",
      "包裹块内必须包含一条 <journal_entry>...</journal_entry>。",
      "状态、情绪和记忆的更新为可选项，但必须保留在 <mnemosyne_meta> 内部。"
    ],
    "active_push_template": [
      "当前本地时间：{{current_time}}",
      "你正在判断是否在幕后时间结束后主动向用户发起消息。",
      "请遵循 system_prompt 中的角色人设，保持自然。",
      "最新日志：",
      "{{latest_journal_text}}",
      "角色状态 JSON：",
      "{{character_state_json}}",
      "",
      "先输出一段简短自然的可见消息。",
      "然后输出唯一一个 <mnemosyne_meta>...</mnemosyne_meta> 包裹块。",
      "若无任何内容变更，输出 <mnemosyne_meta></mnemosyne_meta>。",
      "所有隐藏块必须保留在 <mnemosyne_meta> 内部。"
    ]
  },
  "hidden_blocks": [
    {
      "name": "mnemosyne_meta",
      "target": "mnemosyne_meta",
      "mode": "text",
      "pattern": "<mnemosyne_meta>([\\s\\S]*?)</mnemosyne_meta>"
    },
    {
      "name": "character_state_patch",
      "target": "character_state_patch",
      "mode": "json",
      "pattern": "<character_state_patch>([\\s\\S]*?)</character_state_patch>"
    },
    {
      "name": "character_emotion_patch",
      "target": "character_emotion_patch",
      "mode": "json",
      "pattern": "<character_emotion_patch>([\\s\\S]*?)</character_emotion_patch>"
    },
    {
      "name": "character_memory_append",
      "target": "character_memory_append",
      "mode": "json",
      "pattern": "<character_memory_append>([\\s\\S]*?)</character_memory_append>"
    },
    {
      "name": "journal_entry",
      "target": "journal_entry",
      "mode": "text",
      "pattern": "<journal_entry>([\\s\\S]*?)</journal_entry>"
    }
  ]
}
